        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure 7. Meterythrops sp. Murano, 1977. Female (ca 25 mm, NSMT-Cr 16813). (A) Sternal process on first to third and fifth to eighth thoracic somites, ventral; (B) right mandible; (C) right maxillule, ventral; (D) right maxilla, ventral; (E) endopod of right first thoracopod; (F) endopod of right second thoracopod; (G) right third thoracopod; (H) endopod of right eighth thoracopod; (I) uropod, ventral; (J) spiniation on statocyst region of uropodal endopod, ventral; (K) uropod and telson, dorsal." ;
